{"type":"tool_use","timestamp":1775811084199,"sessionID":"ses_2896b9041ffedvpYdRzp5w33Sh","part":{"id":"prt_d7694a3d8001KVViRutqw3wZqS","messageID":"msg_d76947e64001l8hG1Howb65mXh","sessionID":"ses_2896b9041ffedvpYdRzp5w33Sh","type":"tool","tool":"task","callID":"call_0d1a5abe6d434275bf22f25d","state":{"status":"completed","input":{"description":"Explore agentcube project structure","prompt":"Explore the agentcube project at /home/dsj/benchmark to understand:\n\n1. The overall project structure - look at top-level directories\n2. The pkg/apis directory structure if it exists\n3. Any existing proposal.md files to understand the format/convention\n4. Any existing CRD type definitions, especially in pkg/apis/runtime/\n5. Look for any shared types or constants patterns already in use\n6. Check for any existing scheme registration, GroupVersion definitions\n7. Look at go.mod for the module path\n\nReturn all findings in detail including file paths and relevant code snippets.","subagent_type":"explore"},"output":"task_id: ses_2896b49aaffebvCKKRBYG60kUd (for resuming to continue this task if needed)\n\n<task_result>\nI now have a comprehensive understanding of the project. Here is my detailed report:\n\n---\n\n## AgentCube Project Exploration Report\n\n### 1. Overall Project Structure\n\nThe agentcube project lives at:\n**`/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_alibaba-cn-qwen3.6-plus_20260410T073331Z/`**\n\nTop-level directory layout:\n\n```\nagentcube/\n├── .sdd_prompt.md\n├── changes/              # AR (Assignment Request) change proposals\n│   ├── AR-001/           # CRD AgentRuntime type definitions\n│   ├── AR-002/           # CRD CodeInterpreter type definitions\n│   └── AR-003/           # CRD shared types and constants\n├── ci-cd/\n├── cli-toolkit/\n├── code-execution/\n├── coverage.out\n├── deployment/           # client-go docs, design, spec\n├── go.mod\n├── go.sum\n├── idle-cleanup/\n├── integrations/\n├── pkg/                  # Go packages (only pkg/apis so far)\n│   └── apis/\n│       └── runtime/\n│           └── v1alpha1/\n├── project.md\n├── python-sdk/\n├── sandbox-orchestration/\n├── session-routing/\n├── session-store/\n├── test_spec.md\n└── testing/\n```\n\n**Project description**: AgentCube is a Kubernetes-native sandbox orchestration platform for AI agents. It provisions isolated sandbox pods on demand, routes HTTP traffic through session-aware proxies, and manages lifecycle (creation, expiry, idle cleanup).\n\n---\n\n### 2. pkg/apis Directory Structure\n\n```\npkg/apis/\n└── runtime/\n    └── v1alpha1/\n        ├── agent_type.go                  # AgentRuntime CRD types\n        ├── agent_type_test.go             # Tests for AgentRuntime types\n        ├── codeinterpreter_types.go       # CodeInterpreter CRD types\n        ├── codeinterpreter_types_test.go  # Tests for CodeInterpreter types\n        ├── doc.go                         # +k8s:deepcopy-gen and +groupName markers\n        ├── groupversion_info.go           # GroupVersion, SchemeBuilder, AddToScheme\n        ├── groupversion_info_test.go      # Scheme registration tests\n        ├── register.go                    # Kind constants, Resource() helper\n        ├── register_test.go               # GroupVersion constant tests\n        └── zz_generated.deepcopy.go       # Auto-generated DeepCopy methods\n```\n\nThere is currently only **one API group** (`runtime`) with **one version** (`v1alpha1`).\n\n---\n\n### 3. Existing proposal.md Files\n\nThere are **three proposal files** in the `changes/` directory, each following a consistent format:\n\n**File: `/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_alibaba-cn-qwen3.6-plus_20260410T073331Z/changes/AR-001/proposal.md`**\n- Title: `# AR-001: CRD AgentRuntime 类型定义`\n- Sections: Overview, Metadata (Module, Language, Size), Purpose, Scope (In/Out), Type Definition Summary (ASCII tree), Impact Analysis (direct/downstream/no-impact), Alternatives (A/B/C/D with pros/cons), Acceptance Criteria, Status checkboxes\n\n**File: `/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_alibaba-cn-qwen3.6-plus_20260410T073331Z/changes/AR-002/proposal.md`**\n- Title: `# AR-002: CRD CodeInterpreter 类型定义`\n- Same structure, adds a \"Differences from AgentRuntime\" comparison table\n\n**File: `/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_alibaba-cn-qwen3.6-plus_20260410T073331Z/changes/AR-003/proposal.md`**\n- Title: `# AR-003: CRD 共享类型与常量`\n- Same structure, focuses on extracting shared types (`TargetPort`, `ProtocolType`, `AuthModeType`)\n\nAdditionally, there is a benchmark-level proposal at `/home/dsj/benchmark/proposal.md` (AR-001 CRD AgentRuntime type definitions with a more detailed English format including Design, Impact Analysis, Alternatives, Dependencies, Verification sections).\n\n---\n\n### 4. Existing CRD Type Definitions in pkg/apis/runtime/\n\n#### 4.1 AgentRuntime Types (`agent_type.go`)\n\n**File**: `/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_alibaba-cn-qwen3.6-plus_20260410T073331Z/pkg/apis/runtime/v1alpha1/agent_type.go`\n\n```go\n// +genclient\n// +k8s:deepcopy-gen:interfaces=k8s.io/apimachinery/pkg/runtime.Object\n// +kubebuilder:object:root=true\n// +kubebuilder:subresource:status\n// +kubebuilder:resource:scope=Namespaced,plural=agentruntimes\n// +kubebuilder:printcolumn:name=\"Age\",type=\"date\",JSONPath=\".metadata.creationTimestamp\"\ntype AgentRuntime struct {\n    metav1.TypeMeta   `json:\",inline\"`\n    metav1.ObjectMeta `json:\"metadata,omitempty\"`\n    Spec   AgentRuntimeSpec   `json:\"spec\"`\n    Status AgentRuntimeStatus `json:\"status,omitempty\"`\n}\n\ntype AgentRuntimeSpec struct {\n    Ports              []TargetPort     `json:\"targetPort,omitempty\"`\n    Template           *SandboxTemplate `json:\"podTemplate\"`\n    SessionTimeout     *metav1.Duration `json:\"sessionTimeout,omitempty\"`\n    MaxSessionDuration *metav1.Duration `json:\"maxSessionDuration,omitempty\"`\n}\n\ntype SandboxTemplate struct {\n    Labels      map[string]string `json:\"labels,omitempty\"`\n    Annotations map[string]string `json:\"annotations,omitempty\"`\n    Spec        corev1.PodSpec    `json:\"spec\"`\n}\n\ntype AgentRuntimeStatus struct {\n    Conditions []metav1.Condition `json:\"conditions,omitempty\"`\n}\n\ntype AgentRuntimeList struct { ... }\n\nfunc init() {\n    SchemeBuilder.Register(&AgentRuntime{}, &AgentRuntimeList{})\n}\n```\n\n#### 4.2 CodeInterpreter Types (`codeinterpreter_types.go`)\n\n**File**: `/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_alibaba-cn-qwen3.6-plus_20260410T073331Z/pkg/apis/runtime/v1alpha1/codeinterpreter_types.go`\n\n```go\ntype ProtocolType string\nconst (\n    ProtocolTypeHTTP  ProtocolType = \"HTTP\"\n    ProtocolTypeHTTPS ProtocolType = \"HTTPS\"\n)\n\ntype AuthModeType string\nconst (\n    AuthModePicoD AuthModeType = \"picod\"\n    AuthModeNone  AuthModeType = \"none\"\n)\n\ntype TargetPort struct {\n    PathPrefix string       `json:\"pathPrefix,omitempty\"`\n    Name       string       `json:\"name,omitempty\"`\n    Port       uint32       `json:\"port\"`\n    Protocol   ProtocolType `json:\"protocol\"`\n}\n\ntype CodeInterpreter struct { ... }   // namespaced CRD with status subresource\ntype CodeInterpreterSpec struct {\n    Ports              []TargetPort                    `json:\"ports,omitempty\"`\n    Template           *CodeInterpreterSandboxTemplate `json:\"template\"`\n    SessionTimeout     *metav1.Duration                `json:\"sessionTimeout,omitempty\"`\n    MaxSessionDuration *metav1.Duration                `json:\"maxSessionDuration,omitempty\"`\n    WarmPoolSize       *int32                          `json:\"warmPoolSize,omitempty\"`\n    AuthMode           AuthModeType                    `json:\"authMode,omitempty\"`\n}\ntype CodeInterpreterStatus struct {\n    Conditions []metav1.Condition `json:\"conditions,omitempty\"`\n    Ready      bool               `json:\"ready,omitempty\"`\n}\ntype CodeInterpreterSandboxTemplate struct {\n    Labels           map[string]string             `json:\"labels,omitempty\"`\n    Annotations      map[string]string             `json:\"annotations,omitempty\"`\n    RuntimeClassName *string                       `json:\"runtimeClassName,omitempty\"`\n    Image            string                        `json:\"image,omitempty\"`\n    ImagePullPolicy  corev1.PullPolicy             `json:\"imagePullPolicy,omitempty\"`\n    ImagePullSecrets []corev1.LocalObjectReference `json:\"imagePullSecrets,omitempty\"`\n    Environment      []corev1.EnvVar               `json:\"environment,omitempty\"`\n    Command          []string                      `json:\"command,omitempty\"`\n    Args             []string                      `json:\"args,omitempty\"`\n    Resources        corev1.ResourceRequirements   `json:\"resources,omitempty\"`\n}\ntype CodeInterpreterList struct { ... }\n\nfunc init() {\n    SchemeBuilder.Register(&CodeInterpreter{}, &CodeInterpreterList{})\n}\n```\n\n---\n\n### 5. Shared Types and Constants Patterns\n\nCurrently, shared types (`ProtocolType`, `AuthModeType`, `TargetPort`) are defined in `codeinterpreter_types.go` and implicitly shared with `agent_type.go` (same package). AR-003 proposes extracting these into a dedicated `shared_types.go` file.\n\n**Pattern for string-based enums**:\n```go\ntype ProtocolType string\nconst (\n    ProtocolTypeHTTP  ProtocolType = \"HTTP\"\n    ProtocolTypeHTTPS ProtocolType = \"HTTPS\"\n)\n```\n\n**Pattern for shared structs**: `TargetPort` is used by both `AgentRuntimeSpec.Ports` and `CodeInterpreterSpec.Ports`.\n\n**Note**: The proposal (`proposal.md` at benchmark root) shows `TargetPort` with `*string` pointer fields for `PathPrefix` and `Name`, but the current implementation uses plain `string`. This is a discrepancy between the proposal and implementation.\n\n---\n\n### 6. Scheme Registration and GroupVersion Definitions\n\n#### 6.1 doc.go\n**File**: `/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_alibaba-cn-qwen3.6-plus_20260410T073331Z/pkg/apis/runtime/v1alpha1/doc.go`\n```go\n// +k8s:deepcopy-gen=package\n// +groupName=runtime.agentcube.volcano.sh\npackage v1alpha1\n```\n\n#### 6.2 groupversion_info.go\n**File**: `/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_alibaba-cn-qwen3.6-plus_20260410T073331Z/pkg/apis/runtime/v1alpha1/groupversion_info.go`\n```go\npackage v1alpha1\n\nimport (\n    \"k8s.io/apimachinery/pkg/runtime/schema\"\n    \"sigs.k8s.io/controller-runtime/pkg/scheme\"\n)\n\nvar (\n    GroupVersion = schema.GroupVersion{Group: \"runtime.agentcube.volcano.sh\", Version: \"v1alpha1\"}\n    SchemeBuilder = &scheme.Builder{GroupVersion: GroupVersion}\n    AddToScheme = SchemeBuilder.AddToScheme\n)\n```\n\n#### 6.3 register.go\n**File**: `/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_alibaba-cn-qwen3.6-plus_20260410T073331Z/pkg/apis/runtime/v1alpha1/register.go`\n```go\npackage v1alpha1\n\nimport \"k8s.io/apimachinery/pkg/runtime/schema\"\n\nvar (\n    CodeInterpreterKind             = \"CodeInterpreter\"\n    CodeInterpreterGroupKind        = GroupVersion.WithKind(\"CodeInterpreter\")\n    CodeInterpreterListKind         = \"CodeInterpreterList\"\n    CodeInterpreterGroupVersionKind = GroupVersion.WithKind(\"CodeInterpreter\")\n)\n\nvar (\n    AgentRuntimeKind             = \"AgentRuntime\"\n    AgentRuntimeListKind         = \"AgentRuntimeList\"\n    AgentRuntimeGroupVersionKind = GroupVersion.WithKind(\"AgentRuntime\")\n)\n\nvar SchemeGroupVersion = GroupVersion\n\nfunc Resource(resource string) schema.GroupVersionResource {\n    return GroupVersion.WithResource(resource)\n}\n```\n\n#### 6.4 Registration via init()\nEach type file registers itself with the SchemeBuilder in an `init()` function:\n```go\nfunc init() {\n    SchemeBuilder.Register(&AgentRuntime{}, &AgentRuntimeList{})\n}\nfunc init() {\n    SchemeBuilder.Register(&CodeInterpreter{}, &CodeInterpreterList{})\n}\n```\n\n---\n\n### 7. go.mod Module Path\n\n**File**: `/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_alibaba-cn-qwen3.6-plus_20260410T073331Z/go.mod`\n\n```\nmodule github.com/volcano-sh/agentcube\n\ngo 1.24.4\n\nrequire (\n    github.com/stretchr/testify v1.11.1\n    k8s.io/api v0.34.1\n    k8s.io/apimachinery v0.34.1\n    sigs.k8s.io/controller-runtime v0.22.2\n)\n```\n\n**Key dependencies**:\n| Dependency | Version | Purpose |\n|---|---|---|\n| `k8s.io/api` | v0.34.1 | `corev1.PodSpec`, `corev1.EnvVar`, `corev1.PullPolicy`, etc. |\n| `k8s.io/apimachinery` | v0.34.1 | `metav1.TypeMeta`, `metav1.ObjectMeta`, `metav1.Duration`, `metav1.Condition`, `schema.GroupVersion` |\n| `sigs.k8s.io/controller-runtime` | v0.22.2 | `scheme.Builder` for scheme registration |\n| `github.com/stretchr/testify` | v1.11.1 | Testing assertions |\n\n---\n\n### Summary of Key Patterns\n\n1. **API Group**: `runtime.agentcube.volcano.sh`, Version: `v1alpha1`\n2. **File organization**: One file per CRD type (`agent_type.go`, `codeinterpreter_types.go`), plus `doc.go`, `groupversion_info.go`, `register.go`, and `zz_generated.deepcopy.go`\n3. **Kubebuilder markers**: `+genclient`, `+k8s:deepcopy-gen:interfaces=...`, `+kubebuilder:object:root=true`, `+kubebuilder:subresource:status`, `+kubebuilder:resource:scope=Namespaced`, `+kubebuilder:printcolumn`\n4. **Scheme registration**: Uses `sigs.k8s.io/controller-runtime/pkg/scheme` Builder pattern, with per-type `init()` registration\n5. **Kind constants**: Defined in `register.go` as package-level vars (e.g., `AgentRuntimeKind`, `AgentRuntimeGroupVersionKind`)\n6. **Shared types**: Currently in `codeinterpreter_types.go`, with AR-003 proposing extraction to `shared_types.go`\n7. **Testing**: Comprehensive table-driven and unit tests using `stretchr/testify/assert`, covering defaults, DeepCopy isolation, nil field handling, and scheme registration\n</task_result>","metadata":{"sessionId":"ses_2896b49aaffebvCKKRBYG60kUd","model":{"modelID":"qwen3.6-plus","providerID":"alibaba-cn"},"truncated":false},"title":"Explore agentcube project structure","time":{"start":1775810950738,"end":1775811084195}}}}
